{"tid":1391921,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長期提供糧餉比612人道支援基金","createTime":"2019-07-31T14:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T18:24:41.000Z","uid":295768,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"977caef842830e2837c29534d83056528d1c16ea","tid":1391921,"uid":295768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:48:43.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係一名和理非的IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我諗到一個方法想長期提供糧餉比612人道支援基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個計劃就叫做「內容農場 - 香港加油版」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWhat?<br />\n就是成立一個blog/網站將近來發生的新聞及真實影片全部放上去，加埋Google 廣告，香港人利用每日搭車等車去廁所時間，用手機按這個網站廣告，產生的廣告收入全數捐款比612人道支援基金<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWhy?<br />\n近來的捐款只能應付短期用來購買物資及法律援助等，但香港人都有生活支出，不能長期地捐款下去；所以這個計劃的定位是 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">長期</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">穩定地</span></span> 提供現金流 比612人道支援基金之用，當然也可以作為備份新聞之用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHow?<br />\n利用不同devices如手機，桌面電腦，在不同時間，不同地方上這個網站，按下廣告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為我只有一個人，現階段我諗到將每日的 Google Analyse 數據 screen capture 放上連登，因為 Google ad 要儲夠一定數目，才能將錢滙出（註1），然之後我會用私人銀行帳戶捐到 612 人道支援基金，但這個方法只能講個信字，除左我用私人銀行帳戶，還有沒有其他方法捐會更合適？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n註1<br />\n當Adsense廣告收入超過100美元金的時候. Google就會將這一筆錢透過指定的管道發送. 目前較常用的取款途徑是利用西聯匯款,支票和電匯的方式.<br />\nref: <a href=\"https://affnotes.com/google-adsense-making-money/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faffnotes.com%2Fgoogle-adsense-making-money%2F&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=1c71233c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://affnotes.com/google-adsense-making-money/</a><br />\n<br />\n註2<br />\n一萬元的月收入大約需要一百萬月瀏覽量<br />\nref: <a href=\"https://upsangel.com/webhosting-seo/4-year-google-adsense-experience/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupsangel.com%2Fwebhosting-seo%2F4-year-google-adsense-experience%2F&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=8bf4cbb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://upsangel.com/webhosting-seo/4-year-google-adsense-experience/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家唔覺得依條Q WORK 唔work? 求教各位高手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3bf745768be4346dcf61f00d6a15a5bdc4a56a","tid":1391921,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n5/8 九巴不合作運動 正式啟動！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/abDpOOU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/abDpOOU</a><br />\n<br />\nTG group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFlpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=b530c426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA</a>"},{"pid":"fc098f1b2c8082c79b1c18e20fa7f69d2158d434","tid":1391921,"uid":269703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"977caef842830e2837c29534d83056528d1c16ea","tid":1391921,"uid":295768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:48:43.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係一名和理非的IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我諗到一個方法想長期提供糧餉比612人道支援基金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個計劃就叫做「內容農場 - 香港加油版」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWhat?<br />\n就是成立一個blog/網站將近來發生的新聞及真實影片全部放上去，加埋Google 廣告，香港人利用每日搭車等車去廁所時間，用手機按